Maven Wrapper Allows you to run maven without having specific version of maven installed on specific machine

Command to install maven wrapper:

    mvn -N io.takari:maven:wrapper

To install the Specific Version of Maven Wrapper:

    mvn -N io.takari:maven:wrapper -Dmaven=3.6.0

now if you do ./mvnw --version   ---> this will give you maven wrapper version


Its a good practice to use Maven Wrapper as it makes your project portable


